娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield) 通过重新发行黑胶唱片和伦敦特别演出来庆祝《Unwriting》20 周年https://www.nme.com/news/music/natasha-bedingfield-to-celebrate-20th-anniversary-of-unwriting-with-vinyl-re-release-and-special-london-show-3752234?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=natasha-bedingfield 庆祝未成文与乙烯基重新发行和特别伦敦演出 20 周年Anagricel DuranTue, 30 Apr 2024 21:13:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3752234 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Natasha Bedingfield &#39;Unwriting&#39; 专辑艺术作品来源 PRESS" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首主打歌最近在浪漫喜剧电影《Anyone But You》中亮相后，19 年来首次进入排行榜。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/natasha-bedingfield-to-celebrate-20th-anniversary-of-unwritten-with-vinyl-re-release-and-special-london-show-3752234">娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield) 为庆祝《不成文》(Unwriting) 20 周年而发布的帖子，以重新发行黑胶唱片和伦敦特别演出的形式</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Natasha Bedingfield &#39;Unwriting&#39; 专辑艺术作品来源 PRESS" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-album-artwork-credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Natasha-Bedingfield">娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield)</a>宣布将重新发行黑胶唱片《Unwriting》并在伦敦举办演出，以庆祝专辑诞生 20 周年。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/natasha-bedingfield-soundtrack-of-my-life-2709166">《我的生活》原声带：娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德</a></strong></li></ul><p>她 2004 年的首张专辑一经发行就登上了英国排行榜的第一名。这张专辑收录了《These Words》、《Single》、《Wild Horses》和《I Bruise Easy》等热门歌曲。它还收录了歌曲“Unwriting”，该歌曲最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/natasha-bedingfields-unwritten-returns-to-uk-top-20-after-featuring-in-anyone-but-you-3575751">在悉尼·斯威尼和格伦·鲍威尔的浪漫喜剧“<em>除了你以外的任何人”</em>中出现后再次流行</a>。 1 月 12 日，它 19 年来首次进入排行榜，最高排名第 12 位，目前仍稳居前 20 名。</p><p> 《Unwriting》作为专辑中的第三首单曲发行。 2006年，这首歌成为MTV真人秀电视剧<em>《The Hills》</em>的主题曲。它在公告牌百强单曲榜上排名第五，成为贝丁菲尔德首个进入美国前十名的单曲。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Natasha Bedingfield - Unwriting（官方视频）（如《Anyone But You》中的特色）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/b7k0a5hYnSI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在评论这首歌曲的复兴时，贝丁菲尔德说：“我以前在电影中也听过歌曲，但这一次我真的很喜欢它以如此特殊的方式使用，让你感到快乐。人们离开剧院时实际上正在唱这首歌！</p><p> “多年来，‘不成文’已经成为一首值得你大声唱出的赞歌。这让我成为世界上最幸福的女孩，因为我一直觉得一首好的流行歌曲实际上是你可以带的东西。就像一首美妙的足球歌曲！”</p><p>这首歌为贝丁菲尔德赢得了第 49 届格莱美奖最佳流行女歌手和年度专辑的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>提名。 《 <em>Anyone But You》</em>发布后，该视频也在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">TikTok</a>上疯传。</p><p> 《Unwriting》将首次推出黑胶唱片，以庆祝其成立 20 周年。特别版黑胶唱片采用桃色梦幻色黑胶唱片。还将提供标准的黑色压制。两种印刷品都附有一本四页的小册子，其中包含原始 CD 版本中的歌词和图像拼贴画。再版定于 9 月 6 日发行。您可以<a href="http://natashab.lnk.to/UnwrittenVinyl" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订黑胶唱片</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3752237" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3752237" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3752237" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield) 重新发行黑胶唱片《Unwriting》。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1612" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS-400x322.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS-800x645.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS-696x561.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1122.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Natasha-Bedingfield-Unwritten-re-issue-vinyl-pressing.-Credit-PRESS-1068x861.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3752237" class="wp-caption-text">娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield) 重新发行黑胶唱片《Unwriting》。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德“不成文”黑胶唱片曲目列表：</strong></p><p> <strong>A面</strong><br /><strong>这些字</strong><br /><strong>单身的</strong><br /><strong>我是一颗炸弹</strong><br /><strong>不成文</strong><br /><strong>我很容易瘀伤</strong><br /><strong>如果你要跳</strong></p><p><strong>B面</strong><br /><strong>无声电影</strong><br /><strong>我们都以自己的方式疯狂</strong><br /><strong>青蛙和王子</strong><br /><strong>把我放在中间</strong><br /><strong>野马儿</strong></p><p>此外，这位歌手还宣布将于 9 月 12 日在伦敦 KOKO 举办一场特别的头条演出，以庆祝她的首张专辑发行 20 周年。门票预售将于英国夏令时间 5 月 1 日星期三上午 10 点开始。一般门票销售将于英国夏令时间 5 月 3 日星期五上午 10 点开始。请访问此处获取门票并查看下面的完整旅游日期列表。</p><h2> <strong>Natasha Bedingfield 2024 年英国巡演日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>可能</strong><br /><strong>25 - 伯明翰，骄傲节</strong></p><p><strong>六月</strong><br /><strong>第七届剑桥剑桥俱乐部节</strong></p><p><strong>七月</strong><br /><strong>13 – 格拉斯哥，TRNSMT 音乐节</strong></p><p><strong>八月</strong><br /><strong>3 – 沃特福德，All Together Now 音乐节</strong><br /><strong>23 – 科茨沃尔德，盛大的节日</strong><br /><strong>24 - 康沃尔郡，公园音乐节</strong><br /><strong>25 - 朴茨茅斯，胜利节</strong></p><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>12 – 伦敦，科科</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/natasha-bedingfield-to-celebrate-20th-anniversary-of-unwritten-with-vinyl-re-release-and-special-london-show-3752234">娜塔莎·贝丁菲尔德 (Natasha Bedingfield) 为庆祝《不成文》(Unwriting) 20 周年而发布的帖子，以重新发行黑胶唱片和伦敦特别演出的形式</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
